Rating: 3
This is really good, but I made this & the Ginger Pear Sorbet on the same day and I like the pear one waaayyyy better (not all my guests agreed with me, though, but most did). This reminded me almost of frozen lemonade (but better). I LOVE ginger, so I almost doubled the amount and I think it still wasn't gingery enough for me personally. I also cut out 1/2 cup of sugar and found it was still a bit too sweet. I cut up some crystallized ginger as garnish - yummy. Next time I might actually mix little pieces of crystallized ginger in with the sorbet before I serve it.

